PORTRAIT SERIE n•4 🌸: This is Jessica, our new Publicity Officer! 🖊 "Hey everyone, I'm Jess! I'm actually a second year Law student and next year I'll be the Publicity Officer of the society! My role is to work closely with our blogger and Facebook/Instagram editors (Erina - Monica - Andra) to ensure the feed has lots of fashion news and events! 
My love of fashion began at secondary school when I was asked to be in a fashion show. I saw the hard work, preparation and all of the time that went into it and really enjoyed being part of it. My favourite part was when we were given our outfits and I literally wanted them all! Shortly after I won a Givenchy bag at a charity auction and then my obsession with designer bags came in...
My aim is to become an IP Lawyer specialising in Fashion, as it allows me to merge two major passions of mine. 
If you have any comments on our social medias pages/ want to see more of anything, please let me know!" #new #committee #welcome #tothekclfashionsocfamily #love #fashion #publicityofficer  #becauseKCLFS #kclfashionsoc #kcl
